posts.subject: Dead inside blog
posts.body: There's this zeronet blog called the dead inside blog containing a suicidal person's posts [http://127.0.0.1:43110/14m2AuzoWetHiJFR8SAee4zCN1SjLD6mEv/](http://127.0.0.1:43110/14m2AuzoWetHiJFR8SAee4zCN1SjLD6mEv/). I stumbled upon the blog while it was still active in may of 2018. After expressing his intent of going through with the suicide, he stopped posting. Does /b/ think he took his own life, or just ditched the blog?
